Camera roll is a gallery for viewing photos and videos.

Camera roll is used to view photos of some common formats like Jpeg and PNG and also play videos. Pictures and Albums can be sorted  by date, size and name. Themes, Column counts and viewing styles can be choosen from in the settings.
Pictures can be shared, copied, moved and there is an editing tool for cropping. Wallpapers can be set directly from the app.

Camera roll is also available for third party utility for previewing images and playing video. Overall camera roll is perfect for daily usage.

Camera roll contains no ads and it is fully opensource making it the ideal gallery app.
